"`\\n   128→    APICallCount        int         `json:\\\"api_call_count\\\"`\\n   129→    SubagentTokens      *TokenUsage `json:\\\"subagent_tokens,omitempty\\\"`\\n   130→}\\n   131→```\\n   132→\\n   133→### Strategy-Level Operations\\n   134→\\n   135→Strategies compose low-level primitives into higher-level workflows.\\n   136→\\n   137→**Manual-commit** has condensation logic:\\n   138→\\n   139→```go\\n   140→// CondenseSession reads accumulated temporary state and writes a committed checkpoint.\\n   141→func (s *ManualCommitStrategy) CondenseSession(\\n   142→    repo *git.Repository,\\n   143→    checkpointID id.CheckpointID,\\n   144→    state *SessionState,\\n   145→) (*CondenseResult, error)\\n   146→```\\n   147→\\n   148→## Storage\\n   149→\\n   150→| Type | Location | Contents |\\n   151→|------|----------|----------|\\n   152→| Session State | `.git/entire-sessions/<id>.json` | Active session tracking |\\n   153→| Temporary | `entire/<commit[:7]>-<worktreeHash[:6]>` branch | Full state (code + metadata) |\\n   154→| Committed | `entire/checkpoints/v1` branch (sharded) | Metadata + commit reference |\\n   155→\\n   156→### Session State\\n   157→\\n   158→Location: `.git/entire-sessions/<session-id>.json`\\n   159→\\n   160→Stored in git common dir (shared across worktrees). Tracks active session info.\\n   161→\\n   162→### Temporary Checkpoints\\n   163→\\n   164→Branch: `entire/<commit[:7]>-<worktreeHash[:6]>`\\n   165→\\n   166→Contains full worktree snapshot plus metadata overlay. **Multiple concurrent sessions** can share the same shadow branch - their checkpoints interleave:\\n   167→\\n   168→```\\n   169→<worktree files...>\\n   170→.entire/metadata/<session-id-1>/\\n   171→├── full.jsonl           # Session 1 transcript\\n   172→├── prompt.txt           # User prompts\\n   173→├── context.md           # Generated context\\n   174→└── tasks/<tool-use-id>/ # Task checkpoints\\n   175→.entire/metadata/<session-id-2>/\\n   176→├── full.jsonl   